title: Mu Du Noodles
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Chinese, Organic, Beer/Wine, Asian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Menu changes seasonally, and several mains and appetizers can be prepared vegan upon request. Main entrees comes with brown rice, jasmine rice, or noodle and are topped with vegetable and sauce. Uses some organic ingredients, recycles waste, and purchase renewable energy. Pine tables and chairs and sparse decor on warmly painted walls create a cozy atmosphere.
